  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors are assessed; the declared assurance level is Medium and the decision is Accepted. Note: multiple factors carry achievedLevel below requiredLevel, including at least one factor where the gap is critical, making the Medium assurance declaration and Accepted outcome structurally unsupported.",
