      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification via method of manufactured solutions (MMS) must be demonstrated for all governing equations relevant to hemolysis transport at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "MMS was applied to the Navier-Stokes solver; the scalar hemolysis transport equation was not subjected to independent MMS verification. Achieved Gradation 3."
    },
