      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted at a single operating point only. GCI values at the remaining four operating points are extrapolated from the single-point study without independent verification. Achieved Gradation 2 — three levels below the required Gradation 5 for MRL 5 absolute hemolysis prediction."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
