      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence criteria and round-off error bounds must be documented and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence targets were set at 1e-4 for momentum equations; hemolysis scalar residuals were not separately monitored. Round-off error analysis was not performed. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
