      "acceptanceCriteria": "Boundary conditions applied in the CFD model must be demonstrated equivalent to those measured in the validation experiment at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow rate and rotational speed boundary conditions are matched to experimental measurements within 1%. Outlet pressure boundary condition was set to a nominal value not directly measured in the experiment. Achieved Gradation 3."
